title: Chronic Future Discography
description:
This is (as far as I know) the most complete Discography of my personal favorite band Chronic Future on the internet. I have spent many hours over the past few years digging for new demos and old songs to create this very torrent.Please spread this torrent and get this band the recognition it deserved years ago. 

IMPORTANT NOTE

If you have a demo or a song that I do not have in this Torrent send it to me ASAP and i will listen to it, enjoy it, then promptly add it to the discography.
The only song I know of that I do not have is the Sometimes Demo.

THANK YOU 
ENJOY
